:

1. *Nikom* nije bilo jasno zašto je on to učinio. (No one understood why he did it.)
2. On je bio potpuno nepoznat *nikom*. (He was completely unknown to anyone.)
3. *Nikom* nije dozvoljeno da uđe u tu zgradu. (Nobody is allowed to enter that building.)
4. On je nikom nepoznat. (He is unknown to anyone.)
5. On nikome nije rekao ništa. (He told nobody anything.)